name: Another world
description:
Truly inspired by MC Escher, I decided to make my own reinterpretation of his woodcut creation.

It depicts a cubic architectural structure made from brick. The structure is a paradox with an open archway on each of the five visible sides of the cube.

I created a melancholic touch, by adding characters, and playing on the ambiance. It gives a feeling of an eternal wait, a poetic loneliness.
